verbose_text: While the precise signaling involved in the cytotoxicity of Tnv-6 to CLL cells remains to be elucidated, our studies demonstrate clearly that Tnv-6, previously thought to mainly mediate p53 mediated apoptotic responses, can be cytotoxic to CLL cells through a novel mechanism, dysregulated autophagy.
